The purpose of this research is to look at how educational videos might affect patient satisfaction and anxiety before Mohs surgery day.

 Patients will be randomized to either: 1) a group that receives educational videos before the visit in addition to standard-of-care written and verbal instructions OR 2) a group that receives only standard-of-care written and verbal instructions.

